high_descs: Face the sink to your right.
Take the knife off of the sink in front of you.
Turn right and face the sink to your left.
Slice the apple in the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the sink to your right.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Turn right and face the sink on your left.
Take an apple slice from the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the fridge in front of you.
Place the apple in the fridge then take it out.
Turn around and face the microwave on top of the stove in front of you.
Place the apple slice in the microwave in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold apple slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn to face the apple in the sink.
Slice the apple in the sink with the knife.
Turn to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn to face the apple slices in the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn around to walk to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn to walk across the room the the microwave.
Put the apple slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple slice to put in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the apple in the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into three pieces.
Look down to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Look down to face the apple in the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple in the sink.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Cool the apple piece in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and cross the room to face the microwave.
Place the apple piece in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a piece of apple and place it in the microwave.
